BBI is nothing but a boring storybook that is being forced on everyone including non-readers.Old age in Africa is not synonymous to retiring from politics.There are no jobs. I went to my mutura joint last Sunday. It is a ritual done for the sake of stomach ministry. I encountered two young men who were engaged in a heated discussion on the Building Bridges Initiative. From a distance, one could have easily mistaken them for a drunken lot and not the future of this nation.  



